text: is a Japanese voice actress from Kanagawa Prefecture who is affiliated with Arts Vision. She played her first main role in 2018 as Akira Ono in the anime television series Hi Score Girl. She is also known for her roles as Kylie in The Magnificent Kotobuki, Uruka Takemoto in We Never Learn and Wise in Do You Love Your Mom and Her Two-Hit Multi-Target Attacks?. ==Filmography== ===Anime=== ;2017 *Love Live!
